{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N002171", "chronotag": "1739874539526", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CF2171", "numeroOrdreDepot": "2171", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0324", "triAmendement": "aioaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaas", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA719640", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845454", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA719558", "PA793716"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Mette,  M.&#160;Balanant et M.&#160;Croizier"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "\u00c9TAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 42", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 42", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 42", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0324C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "CB", "libelleMission": "Culture", "missionRef": "2856"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "Patrimoines", "programmeRef": "422058", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Cr\u00e9ation", "programmeRef": "422060", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Transmission des savoirs et d\u00e9mocratisation de la culture", "programmeRef": "422062", "autorisationEngagement": "500000", "creditPaiement": "500000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Soutien aux politiques du minist\u00e8re de la culture", "programmeRef": "422064", "autorisationEngagement": "-500000", "creditPaiement": "-500000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Amendement de repli.&nbsp;</p><p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; proposer une nouvelle r&#x00E9;partition des cr&#x00E9;dits de la Culture afin d&#x2019;apporter un soutien au patrimoine linguistique. En effet les langues r&#x00E9;gionales sont une partie int&#x00E9;grante de notre culture, de notre histoire et de notre patrimoine comme l&#x2019;indique l&#x2019;article 75-1 de la Constitution. Celles-ci sont en danger d&#x2019;apr&#x00E8;s l&#x2019;UNESCO, l&#x2019;&#x00E9;cole comme l&#x2019;ensemble des politiques culturelles devraient &#x00EA;tre des relais de leur diffusion. Il convient donc d&#x2019;aider &#x00E0; p&#x00E9;renniser la pratique des langues r&#x00E9;gionales. En effet, elles contribuent &#x00E0; la vitalit&#x00E9; de notre territoire en participant &#x00E0; la valorisation de nos traditions et favorisent la transmission d&#x2019;une m&#x00E9;moire.</p><p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement a donc pour objet d'abonder de 500 000 euros les autorisations d&#x2019;engagement et les cr&#x00E9;dits de paiement de l&#x2019;action 3 \"Langue fran&#x00E7;aise et langues de France\" port&#x00E9;e par le programme 361 \"Transmission des savoirs et d&#x00E9;mocratisation de la culture\" ; et de diminuer d&#x2019;autant les cr&#x00E9;dits de l&#x2019;action 7 \"Fonctions de soutien du minist&#x00E8;re\" du programme 224 \"Soutien aux politiques du minist&#x00E8;re de la culture\".</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-28", "datePublication": "2024-11-15", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-06T15:34:06+01:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N002171?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "3", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:ni